<HEADLINE>
WITH REPLAYTV, YOU CAN SET UP YOUR OWN CHANNELS  
 
</HEADLINE>
  
 (RESENDING from March 15 for those needing)   (This 450-word ``separate buy'' story is from ``WORTH'' magazine.
