<HEADLINE>
HOW TO FIND INTELLIGENT LIFE ON THE ONLINE-INVESTING PLANET  
 
</HEADLINE>
  
 (RESENDING from March 15 for those needing)   (This 950-word ``separate buy'' personal-finance story is from
``WORTH'' magazine. To publish this article, it must be purchased
