<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-03-20 02:13 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A7753 &Cx1f; tth-z
r s &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-BKC-GONZAGA-SPI &LR;      03-20 1449
