   1999............255 (For January and February)
</P>
<P>
   Source: U.S. Coast Guard; Haitian rescue statistics for South
Florida.
</P>
<P>
   FOR HAITI, THE U.S. ECONOMIC AID JUST KEEP COMING . . .
</P>
<P>
   1986............$76.1 million
</P>
<P>
   1987............$97.5 million
</P>
