<P>
   FOR HAITI, SIZE DOESN'T MATTER: IT GETS BIGGEST SLICE OF U.S.
ECONOMIC AID PIE IN WESTERN HEMISPHERE:
</P>
<P>
   .......................................................Total........
.............Per Capita
</P>
