<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-03-20 14:24 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A7901 &Cx1f; taf-z
u i &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-ELIMINATE-CHINA-ARMED     03-20 0035
</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-ELIMINATE-CHINA-ARMED-POLICE-NYT </SLUG>
  
<TEXT>
<P>
   EDITORS:
</P>
<P>
   CHINA-ARMED-POLICE (Beijing) will not move in tonight's New York
Times News Service file.
</P>
<P>
   N.Y.Times News Service, Mar. 20.
